sentences: Vikter Duplaix (born October 14, 1969), is an American singer-songwriter, producer, multi-instrumentalist, and DJ.

Duplaix has traditional soul singer's beginnings â€“ being raised in both Philadelphia and Augusta, Georgia singing in church choirs, and later took work programming drum tracks while working at a Philadelphia studio.
On August 31, 2009 Vikter released a new single, "Electric Love."
In 2012, Duplaix curated the singer Bilal's career-spanning mixtape, The Retrospection, featuring songs from his unreleased album Love for Sale.
